    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>49936</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！　クルクル、クルールゥルゥ！！
クリューリュゥリュゥリュゥ～……クッルール！！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kruelle! KruKru, Kruellyruelly!!
Krueylyrullyrulooloo~ ....Kkkkkkkruelle!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50012</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Couleur&gt;は努力屋さんだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Couleur&gt; putting in a lot of effort!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50076</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kruelle!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よし！　わたしたちも&lt;Couleur&gt;に
負けないよう、特訓しよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right then, let's train so &lt;Couleur&gt; doesn't
end up doing all the work!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50284</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>めんどくせー……
テキトーに戦ってりゃいいって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sounds like a pain... What's wrong with
punching a little casual-like sometimes?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ねぇ&lt;Couleur&gt;、
連続攻撃を決めるコツってなあに？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, &lt;Couleur&gt;, what's the secret to 
long combo strings?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50460</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……勝手に始めてるし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...and she's sounded off all on her own.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルッ、クルッ、クルクル～ル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kruu, Kruu, KruKruelle.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>えっと……肘と膝？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right, so... Knees and elbows?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50684</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール、クルール！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kruelle, Bombos!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルーーール！！
それっ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kruuuuuelle!
Hiiiiyah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>50944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルッ！　クルール！！
やぁっ！　とぉおっ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kruu! Kruelle!!
Yah! ToOUH!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>51108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール！！！
てぃやあっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kruelle!!
TeiiiiYAH!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>51276</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_128_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Couleur&gt;もすげーけど……
マネする&lt;Mel&gt;もすごくねー？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Couleur&gt;'s pretty cool, but...
&lt;Mel&gt;'s sick too...even if she's just copying him.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
